snippet.title: [OUTDATED] Pre-Fortress 2 - Beta Scout Grenade Showcase
snippet.description:
Notice: None of the footage seen is final.
Pre-Fortress 2 is a Team Fortress 2 mod that is dedicated to recreating both trailer 1 and 2 experience and also some concept art. We aim to create a accurate and balanced experience of a beta Team Fortress 2.


Discord: https://discord.gg/D3Fzdew
